snippet.textDisplay:
Ani Choying who is Buddhist nun is reciting "Om mani pedme hun" which means "The jewel is in the lotus". Which means that enlightenment is within you... goodness, God, whatever you want to call it.
By chanting the mantra you remind yourself that you have that goodness within you & you can bring about enlightenment.
It is the mantra of Chenrezig, the Buddha of Compassion.
